name: ATE DECENTRALIZED FINANCE
short_description: ATE Decentralized finance is the official token of ATE Capital. ATE token is a decentralized token that uses blockchain technology and operates on smart-contract, which are automated enforceable agreements that in need intermediaries like a bank or lawyer and use online blockchain technology instead.
